{"tid":634640,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"恆管2學生涉校內藏毒被捕","createTime":"2018-04-19T12:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T14:14:35.000Z","uid":120022,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cc163304274a803e2b89f83b3cf1a311ffe453f0","tid":634640,"uid":120022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180419/s00001/1524132885931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2F1524132885931&d=OWCyQHwoF3%2BnFKsP1i8cOMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=c2e58934\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180419%2Fs00001%2F1524132885931&h=277491ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180419/s00001/1524132885931</a><br />\n<br />\n據了解，恆生管理學院在本月12日（上周四）凌晨，有學生在校內懷疑吸毒，被警方拘捕。警方發言人回覆本報查詢時表示，本月12日凌晨約2時，接獲沙田行善里一院校職員報案，指懷疑有人在學生宿舍房間內吸食毒品。警員到場後，在現場檢獲少量懷疑大麻草及懷疑毒品吸食工具，並拘捕兩名分別21歲及22歲男子，涉嫌管有危險藥物。二人獲准保釋候查，須於下月底向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n恆管確認，在4月12日凌晨，校方發現學生宿舍房間有少量懷疑大麻草，即時報警處理。警方事後帶有關人士返警署協助調查。校方強調，非常重視學生操守及宿舍管理，對於任何涉嫌違規行為，都會嚴肅處理"},{"pid":"d78dba3b4b020d7faf3f1c905cec7d8dfe258854","tid":634640,"uid":25952,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:05:29.000Z","msg":"Proud of weed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3d9299a114d378348e87f6a0daa088809ca989","tid":634640,"uid":21488,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:06:50.000Z","msg":"哦...恆管...捉去人道毀滅啦<br />\n8大就比次機會佢地"},{"pid":"6225b7767f2c477a0f268ec08d4afeeb4e7896cc","tid":634640,"uid":14065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"CHILL~"},{"pid":"2673586fac4271766ca4c5168f3ec6af12d472df","tid":634640,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r